<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> For the purposes of applying Regulation (EC) No 2200/97, regard shall be had only to healthy apple trees, pear trees, peach trees and nectarine trees capable of producing a normal crop of apples, pears, peaches and nectarines, but not to cider-apple trees or perry-pear trees. </inglise>
